title: Proposal for a Trust wallet Token syrup pool
body:
i feel its been a while we has the trust wallet token (TWT) syrup pool like the way we used to have it occasionally.

I'm of the proposal that a syrup pull for TWT be integrated, no matter how little the pool is, ut would ignite traders to commit some cakes to the pool
